@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Chatbot UI Flow - Restaurant Discovery

actor User
participant "Chat Interface" as CI
participant "Backend API" as API
participant "Restaurant Cards" as RC

User -> CI: Enter query (e.g. "Find Italian catering in Boston")
CI -> API: Send search request with session ID
API -> CI: Return search response with results
CI -> RC: Display restaurant cards
RC -> User: Show restaurant cards with name, cuisine, price, rating
User -> CI: Click on restaurant card
CI -> RC: Expand card details or show bottom sheet
User -> CI: Continue conversation
CI -> API: Send follow-up query maintaining context
API -> CI: Return updated response
CI -> User: Show new results in chat

note over User, CI
  Context maintained:
  - Location (Boston)
  - Cuisine preference (Italian)
  - Party size (implied)
end note

@enduml